title: Asahi Masuyama
text:
is a Japanese <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player for <a href="Oita%20Trinita">Oita Trinita</a>.
Career.
Masuyama joined <a href="J1%20League">J1 League</a> club <a href="Vissel%20Kobe">Vissel Kobe</a> in 2015.
